        Procedure OnClick
            String  sLabel sGreek sEnglish sLetter sMess sPump
            Integer iMet iMet2 iInt iPos iFound iFS iPms iPump chk1 chk2
            Date    dApo dEos
            Get Label to sLabel
            Get Checked_State Of ChkPms     to chk1
